            "id": "PRRC_kwDOIvux3s7WBkzY",
            "body": "<a href=\"#\"><img alt=\"P2\" src=\"https://greptile-static-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/badges/p2.svg?v=9\" align=\"top\"></a> **Plugin-packages phase has implicit dependency on `Plugins` step that `--only` doesn't encode**\n\nThe plugin-packages phase (step 9.5) is gated solely by `!skip.contains(&BootstrapPart::Packages)`. When a user runs `mise bootstrap --only packages`, `Plugins` is placed into the skip set but `Packages` is not, so the plugin-packages loop runs against plugins that were never installed. The driver's `resolve_managers` will then emit \"declared in [bootstrap.plugins] but not installed; run `mise bootstrap`\" for every plugin entry \u2014 confusingly advising users to run the very command they just ran.\n\n<a href=\"https://app.greptile.com/ide/claude-code?prompt=This%20is%20a%20comment%20left%20during%20a%20code%20review.%0APath%3A%20src%2Fcli%2Fbootstrap.rs%0ALine%3A%20757-780%0A%0AComment%3A%0A**Plugin-packages%20phase%20has%20implicit%20dependency%20on%20%60Plugins%60%20step%20that%20%60--only%60%20doesn't%20encode**%0A%0AThe%20plugin-packages%20phase%20%28step%209.5%29%20is%20gated%20solely%20by%20%60!skip.contains%28%26BootstrapPart%3A%3APackages%29%60.%20When%20a%20user%20runs%20%60mise%20bootstrap%20--only%20packages%60%2C%20%60Plugins%60%20is%20placed%20into%20the%20skip%20set%20but%20%60Packages%60%20is%20not%2C%20so%20the%20plugin-packages%20loop%20runs%20against%20plugins%20that%20were%20never%20installed.%20The%20driver's%20%60resolve_managers%60%20will%20then%20emit%20%22declared%20in%20%5Bbootstrap.plugins%5D%20but%20not%20installed%3B%20run%20%60mise%20bootstrap%60%22%20for%20every%20plugin%20entry%20%E2%80%94%20confusingly%20advising%20users%20to%20run%20the%20very%20command%20they%20just%20ran.%0A%0AHow%20can%20I%20resolve%20this%3F%20If%20you%20propose%20a%20fix%2C%20please%20make%20it%20concise.&repo=jdx%2Fmise&pr=11024&platform=github\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https:/