            "id": "PRRC_kwDOIvux3s7WBiuh",
            "body": "### Plugins apply before config refresh\n\n**High Severity**\n\n<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->\n`apply_bootstrap_plugins` runs once at bootstrap start using the initial merged config, while plugin-managed `[bootstrap.packages]` are applied later after dotfiles (with `Config::reset`) and `mise install`. `[bootstrap.plugins]` that only appear after those steps are never installed on the first `mise bootstrap` run, so the late plugin-package phase sees declared managers that are still missing.\n<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->\n\n<!-- BUGBOT_BUG_ID: f84f30d5-52fe-4b28-8d84-4baa4fcd8001 -->\n\n<!-- LOCATIONS START\nsrc/cli/bootstrap.rs#L539-L544\nsrc/cli/bootstrap.rs#L756-L777\nLOCATIONS END -->\n<details>\n<summary>Additional Locations (1)</summary>\n\n- [`src/cli/bootstrap.rs#L756-L777`](https://github.com/jdx/mise/blob/00798656ee0ecab8f617c8755e73afc4242da776/src/cli/bootstrap.rs#L756-L777)\n\n</details>\n\n<div><a href=\"https://cursor.com/open?REDACTED\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-light.png\"><img alt=\"Fix in Cursor\" width=\"115\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?REDACTED\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-light.png\"><img alt=\"Fix in Web\" width=\"99\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-dark.png\"></picture></a></div>\n\n\n<sup>Reviewed by [Cursor Bugbot](https://cursor.com/bugbot) for commit 00798656ee0ecab8f617c8755e73afc4242da776. Configure [here](htt